20 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 858-351, is
21 amended to read as follows:
22 Section 858-351. Unless the context clearly indicates
23 otherwise, as used in Sections 858-351 through 858-363 of The
24 Oklahoma Real Estate License Code and Section 3 of this act:
