1 4. 6. “Transaction” means an activity or process to buy, sell,
2 lease, rent, option, or exchange real estate. Such activities or
3 processes may include, without limitation, soliciting, advertising,
4 showing, or viewing real property, presenting offers or
5 counteroffers, entering into agreements, and closing such
